name: Red Zebra Bag
description: You,ll step out in style with this Hot little red number. Made from red paton leather and zebra print cowhide this fabulous bag is just what you need for a night out on the town. Plenty of room for the essentials it contains one inner open pocket and one zip pocket, it has a rear zip pocket and comes with an adjustable strap. The entire bag has been hand sewn with waxed thread.

name: Gray Knitted Bag
description: These knitted creations have originated from never worn recycled jumpers. Although not stylish in a past life they have been recreated and made into very cute and practical pieces of art. The knitted fabric has been glued onto a heavy canvas ensuring that the knit does not fray or pull stiches. It has also been lined with a heavy material so the bag does not stretch or loose shape. The interior contains 2 small zip pockets and 1 large zip pocket. The straps are made from deer skin and the bag has been decorated with an assortment of beads. I have had one of these bags years and recently had it drycleaned. It now looks brand new again.

name: Red Leather Satchel
description: With all the new wild shapes and designs in bags these days there is still a demand for the classic satchel. Classic in shape and practical in design. I have designed my satchel for all the basic needs of the modern woman. It has a rear pocket, a pocket for your iphone, front sip pocket, a pocket on the interior and a front pocket for pens etc. Conveiniently shaped so you can easily carry books it also comes with a matching keyring which clips onto the bag. This bag is entirely had sewn with saddlers waxed thread and is the only one or its kind.

name: iphone case
description:
Lost Alien seeks new home.... This cute little alien promises to protect your treasured gadget from breakages and scratches. The pouch is is perfectly moulded to keep a snug fit around your iphone. He has a few friends that are different in colour so if he is not exactly what you want please contact me and I,ll see what I can do.

Measurements 13cm x 8.5cm

name: Black leather Tote
description: For the woman that needs to carry everything this practical piece of art contains 3 inner zip pockets, 3 front pockets and 1 pocket on the back. It has been entirely hand sewn with waxed saddlers thread, Kangaroo thonging has been used for the plaiting and features a piece of crocodile skin down the front of the bag.
